\subsection{Circle of Confusion}
\label{sec:coc}
(see
\href{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circle_of_confusion}{Wikipedia})

The CoC describes the blurring of a point source on the sensor. How
big a CoC is acceptable depends on  the desired resolution.
